<?php snippet('header') ?> <main class="main"> <?php snippet('nav') ?> <header class="hero offpage-hero about-hero"><ul class="hero-socials"><li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/thefortisgroup/?fref=ts"><i class="fa fa-facebook" target="_blank"></i></a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/TheFortisGroup"><i class="fa fa-twitter" target="_blank"></i></a></li><li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/1392417?trk=tyah&trkInfo=clickedVertical%3Acompany%2CclickedEntityId%3A1392417%2Cidx%3A3-2-11%2CtarId%3A1485283024182%2Ctas%3Afortis%20grou"><i class="fa fa-linkedin" target="_blank"></i></a></li><li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC50BfE3X_6S_jGp1ZvhpNAw" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-youtube"></i></a></li><li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/fortisgroupinc/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></a></li></ul><div class="borders"><div class="border-left"></div><div class="border-right"></div><div class="border-bottom"></div></div><div class="hero__content"><h1><span>About</span> Us</h1><h6>When building on a strong foundation, sustainability, accountability, innovation and satisfaction are inherent.</h6></div><div class="hero__content-background"></div></header><!-- End Hero --><section class="about-intro"><div class="about-intro-content"><div class="about-intro-info"><div class="about-intro-video"><h4>Fortis Group</h4><h6>Who We Are.</h6><iframe width="400" height="255" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3t8CTuAMahU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><div class="about-intro-info__content"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/footer-logo.png" draggable="false"><p>Forged from two of Southwestern Ontario’s most trusted names in contracting, Fortis Group is one of the fastest growing companies of its kind across the province. We offer comprehensive contracting solutions with a focus on the retail, commercial, restaurant, institutional, industrial, recreational and automotive sectors. With long histories and deep roots in Design/Build, Contracting and Project Management, Fortis Group has become the first and only choice for many high profile clients across Ontario. Individually we’ve built our reputations by delivering value through diversity and serving as a single source of responsibility. Now collectively, on a solid foundation, we are positioned to continue to grow, succeed and #BuildStrong.</p></div></div><div class="about-ntro-content__redux"><div class="about-intro-cta"><p><strong>Our mission</strong> is to be the leading choice for all construction services in the retail, commercial, restaurant, institutional, industrial, recreational and automotive sectors by consistently delivering unsurpassed project quality, professionalism, client service and integrity. Ultimately, we strive to forge long-term relationships with clients by ensuring a worry-free and seamless experience from concept to completion. This is how we #BuildStrong.</p></div><p>Fortis is committed to the needs and desires of each client and project. We realize that you have many choices when selecting a contractor no matter what the scope or project size. Our desire and primary focus are and always have been, to build strong lasting relationships. As a result of this, we strive for 100% satisfaction and a win-win philosophy.</p></div></div></section><!-- End About Intro --><section class="about-capabilities"><div class="tabs-title"><h4>Capabilities</h4><h6>What We Do.</h6></div><div class="tabsalt"><ul class="tabsalt__nav"><li rel="design">Design/ Build</li><li rel="construction">Construction & Project Management</li><li rel="contracting">General Contracting</li><li rel="renovations">Renovations</li></ul><div class="tabsalt__container"><h6 class="tabalt__drawer" rel="design">Design/ Build</h6><div id="design" class="tabalt__content"><p>Our design/build process utilizes sequential tendering whereby we place components of projects out to bid as drawings are completed and submitted. Our reputation with clients, sub-contractors, trades and workers in the field enables us to offer one of the most comprehensive Design/Build programs in the industry.</p><div class="tabalt-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-1.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab One --><h6 class="tabalt__drawer" rel="construction">Construction & Project Management</h6><div id="construction" class="tabalt__content"><p>At the root of our ability to provide "One Source of Responsibility" is the planning expertise we bring to every project. In the course of construction and project management, we're able to provide unique and innovative solutions that quite often reduce costs for our clients while resulting in projects of the utmost quality, delivered on time every time.</p><div class="tabalt-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-2.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Two --><h6 class="tabalt__drawer" rel="contracting">General Contracting</h6><div id="contracting" class="tabalt__content"><p>Trust us with the execution and completion of your plans. As “one source of responsibility”, we have built a reputation as a leading general contractor for all types of projects. Whether it’s sole source or through competitive bid process, Fortis welcomes the opportunity to demonstrate how we can help you realize your plans exactly as envisioned.</p><div class="tabalt-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-3.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Three --><h6 class="tabalt__drawer" rel="renovations">Renovations</h6><div id="renovations" class="tabalt__content"><p>For some clients, building new simply isn't financially feasible. That's why we also offer complete renovation services for existing facilities. From cosmetic changes and remodeling to full structural upgrades, our team can plan and execute any renovation project for even the most challenging budgets.</p><div class="tabalt-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-4.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Four --></div></div></section><!-- End About Capabilities --><section class="about-cta"><h4>WE'RE NEVER STANDING STILL. <span>SEE WHAT WE'RE UP TO.</span></h4><div class="button-group"><a href="news" class="button"><span></span>Learn More</a></div></section><!-- End About CTA --><section class="about-industries"><div class="tabs-title"><h4>Industries</h4><h6>Who We Work With.</h6></div><div class="tabs"><ul class="tabs__nav"><li rel="retail">Retail & Commercial</li><li rel="restaurant">Restaurant</li><li rel="recreational">Recreational</li><li rel="institutional">Institutional</li><li rel="industrial">Industrial</li><li rel="automotive">Automotive</li></ul><div class="tabs__container"><h6 class="tab__drawer" rel="retail">Retail & Commercial</h6><div id="retail" class="tab__content"><p>Fortis Group specializes in assisting our clients in creating world-class shopping experiences. Our client base includes some of the largest and most successful national retail and commercial brands in the industry along with most major developers and asset managers.</p><div class="tab-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-5.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab One --><h6 class="tab__drawer" rel="restaurant">Restaurant</h6><div id="restaurant" class="tab__content"><p>In restaurant construction, experience is the key and we have taken great measures to ensure our employees, subcontractors and vendors have extensive restaurant construction knowledge and experience. Fortis Group has industry leading expertise and experience in creating bold, distinctive and state-of-the-art dining establishments.</p><div class="tab-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-6.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Two --><h6 class="tab__drawer" rel="recreational">Recreational</h6><div id="recreational" class="tab__content"><p>Our ability to deliver projects on time and on budget has been the deciding factor for many municipalities turning to Fortis Group to construct signature projects that serve their communities.</p><div class="tab-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-7.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Three --><h6 class="tab__drawer" rel="institutional">Institutional</h6><div id="institutional" class="tab__content"><p>Whether it's a school, hospital, retirement home or office building. Fortis Group has the knowledge, skills and resources to design, execute and manage any institutional project to the highest of standards and expectations.</p><div class="tab-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-8.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Four --><h6 class="tab__drawer" rel="industrial">Industrial</h6><div id="industrial" class="tab__content"><p>From fabricating to manufacturing and from warehouse to agricultural, Fortis Group takes pride in its ability to translate complex building requirements into sustainable and efficient building solutions.</p><div class="tab-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-9.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Five --><h6 class="tab__drawer" rel="automotive">Automotive</h6><div id="automotive" class="tab__content"><p>Our standards of craftsmanship and understanding of brand management are unparalleled in the markets that we serve. Fortis Group understands the importance of the delicate balance between image, functionality and value and as such, we have built close, long term relationships with both national and independent dealers.</p><div class="tab-image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1510155538/fortis/cap-10.jpg" draggable="false"></div></div><!-- Tab Six --></div></div></section><!-- End About Industries --></main><!-- End Main --> <?php snippet('footer') ?>